  "texts": [
    "In the vision domain, ViT-3 achieved an accuracy boost of nearly 50% through RKD, outperforming its raw baseline.",
    "These results confirm that student models can retain most of the performance of their teachers while being significantly more efficient and deployable.",
    "This work proposes and validates a cross-modality Recursive Knowledge Distillation (RKD) pipeline applicable to both natural language processing (BERT) and computer vision (ViT) models.",
    "We introduce multi-agent teacher fusion and successive distillation strategies, which significantly improve accuracy in extremely compressed models.3) 4 -34bit Quantization (QLoRA): This stage uses the BitsAndBytesConfig library to load the model in a 4-bit NormalFloat (NF4) Fig 1.1Fig 1.",
